DONAN, TAISSA, and the player sit in the center of the ritual hut. 
They share a bowl of the swamp brew Taissa has concocted. 
Donan reacts as the strange brew takes hold of his senses.
Donan unsteadily gets to his feet.
He begins to hear strange noises... a voice emanating from the darkness surrounding him.
The next three Yorin lines are from other scenes, Donan hears them from his memories as he's hallucinating.
He suddenly recognizes the voice as his son Yorin.
Someone, neither Taissa nor the player, enters the hut and approaches Donan. It is his son.

Donan reaches out to embrace his son, but Yorin steps back. 
He sees his son reject him and it breaks his heart.
There is a long pause. Donan takes a deep breath as he comes to terms with this realization.

Donan erupts into tears, collapsing down onto all fours as sobs wrack his entire body. 
Yorin walks out of the hut and fades into nothingness. This was all in Donanâ€™s mind.
